title: Argentina 2015 nº 009 - BAHIA REDONDA!
text:

Série sobre a minha viagem à ARGENTINA - visitando El Calafate e El Chaltén (Província de Santa Cruz) - Patagônia e San Martin de los Andes (Província de Neuquén) - De 18 de julho a 07 de Agosto de 2015 - Nº 009 ! Series on my trip to ARGENTINA - visiting El Calafate and El Chaltén (Province of Santa Cruz) - Patagonia and San Martin de los Andes (Province of Neuquén) - From July 18th to August 7th 2015 - #009 ! BAHIA REDONDA - LAGO ARGENTINO - EL CALAFATE ! BAÍA REDONDA - LAGO ARGENTINO - EL CALAFATE ! ROUND BAY - ARGENTINO LAKE - EL CALAFATE ! I love cold weather and that's why I decided to go to Southern Argentina on my last vacations!! However, I knew weather in Patagonia can be tough, but I took the risk! Unfortunately I faced bad weather and other problems during my traveling, but, no regrets, because i could see many places I wanted to! There were days that weather was fine and I didn't do anything very special, but enjoyed just as well! That day, for example, I walked along the AVENIDA COSTANERA and saw many interesting natural elements!
